Dick Botiller https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dick_Botiller 0 Dick Botiller (October 26, 1896 – March 24, 1953), sometimes credited as Richard Botiller, was an American character actor of the 1930s and 1940s. While most of his roles were un-credited, many of them nameless as well, he was given more substantial roles occasionally.
